('11027', 0, 'Measurement of Plasma Copper, Ceruloplasmin, Hb, PCV, TEC and TLC in Fasciola hepatica Infestation in Black Bengal Goats', 'Journal', 'nan', 'Measurement of Plasma Copper, Ceruloplasmin, Hb, PCV, TEC and TLC in Fasciola hepatica Infestation in Black Bengal Goats AK Dey - ENVIRONMENT AND ECOLOGY., 2004', '2004', 'AK Dey', 'ENVIRONMENT AND ECOLOGY.', 'MKK PUBLICATIONS', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
