('12975', 0, 'Efficacy of entomopathogenic nematode (Heterorhabditis indica) in controlling phorid Fly, Megaselia sandhui in Agaricus bisporus', 'Journal', 'Copper solution affected the seedling growth in Phaseolus radiatus [Vigna radiata]. Higher concentrations were inhibitory for seed germination and seedling growth in both the cultivars of P. radiatus. Seed germination and seedling growth were maximum at 10 mg/l Cu treated seeds. Concentration above to 10 mg/l inhibit the seed germination and seedling growth in both the cultivars of P. radiatus.', 'Effect of different concentrations of copper on seed germination & seedling growth of Phaseolus radiatus L. cv. PS-16 & K-851 cultivars. S Lokendra, SP Singh, K Anil, V Suman - Plant Archives, 2008', '2008', 'Singh Lokendra, SP Singh, Kumar Anil, Verma Suman', 'Plant Archives', 'Dr RS Yadav', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
