('13107', 1, 'High pressure phase transition and elastic properties of ytterbium compounds YbX (X= O, S, Se and Te)', 'Journal', 'The kinetics and mechanism of oxidation of maltose by periodate in alkaline medium have been investigated. The reaction rate is zero order dependent in [IO4-], while the order with respect to [maltose] and [OH-] is unity. An insignificant effect of change in ionic strength of the medium on the rate has been observed. Activation parameters have been calculated. A suitable mechanistic step and rate expression pertinent to the observed kinetic data are suggested.', 'Kinetics and mechanism of oxidation of maltose by aqueous alkaline solution of periodate Ashish, SP Singh, AK Singh - OXIDATION COMMUNICATIONS, 2005 Cited by 1 Related articles', '2005/1/1', 'Ashish, SP Singh, AK Singh', 'OXIDATION COMMUNICATIONS', 'SCIBULCOM LTD', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
