('13178', 0, 'Two-phase flow instability and bifurcation analysis of inclined multiple uniformly heated channels-15107', 'Journal', 'Various types of precast building components have been developed by various research organisations. These are finding increased acceptance in the building industry. Although technical details and specifications are available in the published form, the scientific and analytical data related to the production of these units are not available for regular production in organised sector. Central Building Research Institute, Roorkee (CBRI) in collaboration with Building Materials and Technology Promotion Council (BMTPC), New Delhi, took up a study to generate production planning data which can be used by production centres using semi-mechanised methods of construction and catering to medium-range housing for efficient and economical manufacturing of these units. Under the project, production planning data in respect of eight walling and roofing units including door and window frames have been generated for …', 'Data base software for production planning of semi-mechanised precast building components. SP Singh, GC Sofat, A Singh, S Chakraverty… - Indian Concrete Journal, 2002 All 2 versions', '2002/3', 'SP Singh, GC Sofat, Ajay Singh, S Chakraverty, Rajeeva Kr Sharma', 'Indian Concrete Journal', 'nan', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
