('13214', 0, 'URINARY LEVELS OF C-TERMINAL CROSSLINKED TELOPEPTIDE TYPE 1 AS A DIAGNOSTIC INDICATOR OF KNEE OSTEOARTHRITIS', 'nan', 'The carrier generation rates of electron-hole pairs in polycrystalline zinc selenide (ZnSe) photovoltaic material have been computed for the first time for AM0, AM1 AM1.5 solar spectra. These theoreticall y computed actual generation rates have heen replaced by a curve filled approximation, which are represented by a series of three exponential terms. A simplified theory has been used for evaluating the solar cell parameters viz. Jsc, Voc, FF and η for the various solar spectra.', 'Polycrystalline ZnSe under solar illumination RN Verma, DP Saha, S Singh - 2001', '2001', 'RN Verma, DP Saha, S Singh', 'nan', 'NISCAIR-CSIR, India', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
