('13243', 0, 'Temporal link prediction in multi-relational network', 'Journal', 'A study was carried out on three tractors of same make and model to know the realistic information on repair and maintenance cost which is directly dependent on the tractor utilization in various operations and handling by the operators for a period of eleven years, i.e., August, 1988 to July, 1999. All the studied tractors were purchased on same date. The tractors T1, T2 & T3 were operated for 5976 hours, 8168 hours and 9670 hours, respectively. These tractors were mainly engaged for seed bed preparation, land development, threshing,/shelling and transportation purposes. The study suggests that an experienced and sincere driver can save the repair-maintenance cost and will also add in enhancing the life of tractor.', 'Effect of utilization and handling of tractors on their repair and maintenance under hilly conditions SP Singh, DK Vatsa, HB Singh - Journal of Agricultural Engineering, 2000 Related articles', '2000', 'SP Singh, DK Vatsa, HB Singh', 'Journal of Agricultural Engineering', 'Indian Society of Agricultural Engineers', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
('13244', 1, 'Mining heterogeneous terrorist attack network using personalized PageRank', 'Journal', 'Linseed cv. Garima was grown in rabi [winter] 1990/91 and 1991/92 with irrigation at IW: CPE (irrigation water: cumulative pan evaporation ratios) 0.4, 0.6 or 0.8, and application of 0-90 kg N/ha as urea. Water use from different soil depths is tabulated. Total water use increased, and water use efficiency decreased slightly, with increasing irrigation. Seed yield increased with increasing irrigation, and in 1991/92 was 694, 765 and 904 kg/ha with irrigation at 0.4, 0.6 and 0.8 IW: CPE. Seed yield, total water use and water use efficiency increased with increasing N rate.', 'Response of linseed to various moisture regimes and nitrogen levels on moisture depletion pattern, consumptive use and water use efficiency. SP Singh, RS Dixit, GR Singh - Environment and Ecology, 2000 Cited by 1 Related articles', '2000', 'SP Singh, RS Dixit, GR Singh', 'Environment and Ecology', 'nan', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
