('13580', 3, 'Absence of CD 9 expression in acute myeloid leukemia: possible correlation with t (8; 21)', 'Journal', 'Results of trials with 2 P. typhoides [= P. americanum] hybrids conducted for 2 seasons to investigate the effect of shading and defoliation on grain yield and its attributes, showed that a reduction in the photosynthetic surface area either by shading or defoliation at anthesis caused reductions in grain number/ear, grain size, rate of grain development and the final grain yield almost in proportion to the reduction in leaf area', 'Studies on the effect of defoliation and shading on grain yield and its components in bajra (Pennisetum typhoides) DVM Rao, SP Singh - Indian Journal of Plant Physiology, 1980 Cited by 3 Related articles All 3 versions', '1980', 'DVM Rao, SP Singh', 'Indian Journal of Plant Physiology', 'nan', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
