('13586', 6, 'TJamSpotter: Real Time Android App for Road Traffic Management.', 'Journal', 'The effect of different zinc concentrations on the self-diffusion of zinc in alkaline and calcareous soils of divergent texture was studied. A linear increase in the self-diffusion coefficient of Zn with increasing concentrations of applied Zn was noted in all the soils. The capacity factor decreased with an increase in concentration of applied Zn. The diffusivity of Zn was higher in fine textured soils as compared to those in coarse textured soils.', 'Diffusion of 65Zn as influenced by rates of applied zinc in soils of divergent texture SP Singh, MK Sinha, NS Randhawa - Journal of the Indian Society of Soil Science, 1980 Cited by 6 Related articles All 6 versions', '1980', 'SP Singh, MK Sinha, NS Randhawa', 'Journal of the Indian Society of Soil Science', 'Indian Society of Soil Science', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0),
