('13668', 0, 'Link prediction using social network analysis over heterogeneous terrorist network', 'Journal', 'The convolution of surface waves in materials with strain-dependent dielectric constants (eg BaTiO 3) is shown to be much larger as compared to piezoelectric materials. A phenomenological theory is developed to derive analytical expressions for the convolved signal output V c. It is found to differ considerably from that for piezoelectric materials as regards the dependent of V c on the frequency of the acoustic waves and the mobility and strength of the DC electric field.', 'The convolution of surface waves in material with strain-dependent dielectric constants SP Singh, AK Agarwal - Journal of Physics D: Applied Physics, 1975 Related articles All 4 versions', '1975/12/1', 'SP Singh, AK Agarwal', 'Journal of Physics D: Applied Physics', 'IOP Publishing', 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0);
